{"tid":2006443,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"新買intel CPU有痕跡？","createTime":"2020-05-07T18:44:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T05:34:44.000Z","uid":69460,"like":0,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"816d07e4205c1f1c1b1f838e44c467d30c741cea","tid":2006443,"uid":69460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T18:44:56.000Z","msg":"買咗9900k 彩盒版開開心心開箱<br />\n個盒有黑色套包住 買時冇睇清楚<br />\n<br />\n返到屋企點知裏面有塊支撐膠版崩咗唔緊要冇所謂<br />\n打開望個CPU表面竟然有痕跡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/isazAqd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FisazAqd.png&h=60ede3bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為用咗濕紙巾不停咁抹 之後先影 冇咁明顯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M2bOEW9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM2bOEW9.jpg&h=b123dca5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本來係咁樣 長方形痕跡 <br />\n唔知係咪生產過程有舊嘢啜實咗導致咁<br />\n<br />\n以為可以抹乾淨<br />\n而家CPU表面長方形痕跡果四個角位由磨砂啞色變咗亮滑面<br />\n雖然好細微 但始終俾咗接近$4000 得唔到完美返嚟個心好唔安樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知對散熱有冇影響<br />\n<br />\n以前買過4790同4790k都未見過咁嘅情況<br />\n請問呢啲情況代理會唔會受理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6e5df90966394a5e932668518f7a74cc0fb69e","tid":2006443,"uid":16230,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:20:43.000Z","msg":"無壞就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a1efc8b35895b315f28690b7c92a62ec2cfc7bc","tid":2006443,"uid":282494,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:22:49.000Z","msg":"好明顯用過喎<br />\n攞返去換啦"},{"pid":"847ba27f64ded18ed588defa244d40816156196b","tid":2006443,"uid":97182,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:26:52.000Z","msg":"試完體質差 再賣俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"787eab1cfb5c715907fa634e5891e3fb912d4b2b","tid":2006443,"uid":69460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ac6e5df90966394a5e932668518f7a74cc0fb69e","tid":2006443,"uid":16230,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:20:43.000Z","msg":"無壞就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:31:30.000Z","msg":"係冇壞但個心有條刺唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n吱散熱膏裝d15唔知有冇影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69eb10c6bd0cb6b2e2018eb371ca8c432f19661","tid":2006443,"uid":3032,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:33:52.000Z","msg":"好似係假貨黎"},{"pid":"61400de07f84dd095b5e8bd07a1606cda2b48497","tid":2006443,"uid":43483,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:34:23.000Z","msg":"賣咸碟咩要用黑膠袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nD痕擺明二手用過啦<br />\n邊間賣咁仆街開佢名啦"},{"pid":"2730bfa32c9cad4ce0cdcfb9c5fa3e28612f868c","tid":2006443,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:35:38.000Z","msg":"聯強貨？"},{"pid":"688c30269b54e5d1b9588bba3f692b5cae339720","tid":2006443,"uid":3032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:36:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/19255/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F19255%2F&d=kJsi%2B77Adq7yP7dZlTZe0BVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=6ad1b120\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkepc.com/19255/</a>"},{"pid":"31838ffd297147c8b0e84df325ba4bba8c170655","tid":2006443,"uid":229100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:38:59.000Z","msg":"真係換啦 <br />\n一睇就知係散熱個印黎"},{"pid":"d24d3a2c8354594808bc02a11337f19ca84c666d","tid":2006443,"uid":69460,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score"